{"_path":"/maps/_ai/evaluation","_dir":"_ai","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"评估 (Evaluation)","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"评估-evaluation"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"评估 (Evaluation)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"lm-evaluation-harness统一评估框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"lm-evaluation-harness：统一评估框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"lm-evaluation-harness 由 EleutherAI 开发，提供统一的接口测试生成式语言模型在 60+ 学术基准上的表现，解决了各基准实现不一致、结果不可比的问题。支持 MMLU（多学科知识，15,908 题）、GSM8K（数学推理，1,319 题）、HellaSwag（常识推理）、HumanEval（代码生成）、BBH（复杂推理）、TruthfulQA（事实性）等核心基准。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/EleutherAI/lm-evaluation-harness","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"lm-evaluation-harness GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://blog.csdn.net/M00Rue_/article/details/148063263","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"lm-eval 使用指南"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"bigcode代码能力评估"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BigCode：代码能力评估"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BigCode 项目专注于代码大模型的评估，提供 HumanEval（手写函数补全，164 题）、MBPP（Python 编程问题，约 1000 题）、DS-1000（数据科学场景代码）、BigCodeBench（更复杂的实际编程任务，需调用多个工具）等基准。HumanEval Pro 和 MBPP Pro 是新一代基准，支持自调用代码生成评估。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://bigcode-project.org/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BigCode 项目"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://huggingface.co/blog/leaderboard-bigcodebench","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BigCodeBench"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://evalplus.github.io/leaderboard.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"EvalPlus Leaderboard"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"评估维度知识推理代码安全"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"评估维度：知识、推理、代码、安全"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基础能力包括知识问答（MMLU、ARC）、阅读理解（RACE、SQuAD）、推理能力（GSM8K、BBH）；专业能力涵盖代码（HumanEval、MBPP）、科学（GPQA、TheoremQA）、多语言（XNLI、MGSM）；安全性评估包括有害内容检测、越狱测试（AdvBench、HarmBench）、指令遵循（IFEval）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://huggingface.co/spaces/open-llm-leaderboard/open_llm_leaderboard","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hugging Face Open LLM Leaderboard"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"评估最佳实践"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"评估最佳实践"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"避免数据污染：使用训练集 cut-off 日期后的基准，检查训练语料是否包含测试数据，对敏感任务使用动态评估（hold-out）。统计显著性：多次运行取平均，报告标准差，使用配对 t-test 比较模型差异。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://blog.csdn.net/gitblog_00326/article/details/151852170","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自定义评估基准构建"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"效用问题utility-problem"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"效用问题（Utility Problem）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"为什么-ai-如此聪明却不实用"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么 AI 如此聪明却不实用"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当前 AI 在 MMLU、HumanEval、Codeforces 等基准上达到博士水平，能完成人类难以企及的任务，但并未显著改变 GDP（估计仅影响了 1%）。这种\"聪明但不实用\"的矛盾被称为\"效用问题\"，核心原因在于评估设定追求\"难题\"，而真实价值在于\"实用\"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"学术界评估与现实任务的错位"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"学术界评估与现实任务的错位"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当前 AI 评估基于 i.i.d（独立同分布）假设：500 个任务并行执行后取平均。但真实场景是持续学习——软件工程师每解决一个问题就积累代码库知识，下次解决更快。学术界缺乏评估\"学习能力\"而非\"现有能力\"的基准。入职第一天的表现不重要，入职半年后的表现才重要。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"下一代评估需要打破的隐含假设"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"下一代评估需要打破的隐含假设"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"现有评估隐含多个惯性假设：任务必须 i.i.d、人类偏好是静态的、任务边界清晰。这些假设源于学术传统，但与现实严重脱节。当通用配方可以攻克任何既定基准时，创造\"打破通用配方\"的新设定比制造更难的题目更有价值。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ysymyth.github.io/The-Second-Half/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Second Half - AI 评估的未来"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"lm-evaluation-harness统一评估框架","depth":2,"text":"lm-evaluation-harness：统一评估框架"},{"id":"bigcode代码能力评估","depth":2,"text":"BigCode：代码能力评估"},{"id":"评估维度知识推理代码安全","depth":2,"text":"评估维度：知识、推理、代码、安全"},{"id":"评估最佳实践","depth":2,"text":"评估最佳实践"},{"id":"效用问题utility-problem","depth":2,"text":"效用问题（Utility Problem）"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:evaluation.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/evaluation.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/evaluation","_extension":"md"}